 in content discovery.</span></div></div></div></div><footer class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__footer\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__footer-actions\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-pack nova-legacy-o-pack--gutter-m nova-legacy-o-pack--width-auto nova-legacy-o-pack--vertical-align-middle\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-pack__item nova-legacy-v-publication-item__footer-button-group\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-button-group nova-legacy-c-button-group--gutter-m nova-legacy-c-button-group--orientation-horizontal nova-legacy-c-button-group--width-auto nova-legacy-v-publication-item__actions\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-button-group__item\"><a class=\"nova-legacy-c-button nova-legacy-c-button--align-center nova-legacy-c-button--radius-m nova-legacy-c-button--size-s nova-legacy-c-button--color-blue nova-legacy-c-button--theme-bare nova-legacy-c-button--width-auto nova-legacy-v-publication-item__action\" href=\"publication/220382600_Usability_engineering_turns_10\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-c-button__label\">View</span></a></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-button-group__item\"><button class=\"nova-legacy-c-button nova-legacy-c-button--align-center nova-legacy-c-button--radius-m nova-legacy-c-button--size-s nova-legacy-c-button--color-blue nova-legacy-c-button--theme-bare nova-legacy-c-button--width-auto nova-legacy-v-publication-item__action\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-c-button__label\"><span class=\" js-lite-click\" data-lite=\"{&quot;click&quot;:[{&quot;t&quot;:&quot;.js-target-abstract-61a68d3838fcf&quot;,&quot;a&quot;:&quot;tc(lite-page-hidden)&quot;},{&quot;t&quot;:&quot;self&quot;,&quot;a&quot;:&quot;tc(lite-page-hidden)&quot;}]}\">Show abstract</span></span></button></div></div></div></div></div></footer></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item publication-citations__item publication-citations__item--redesign\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-citation-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack nova-legacy-o-stack