s have been carried out concerning usage and behaviour (LI and LONGLEY 2006).  ...</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow--body\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow-tip\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-citation-item__context-source\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item nova-legacy-v-publication-item--size-m gtm-citation-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__body\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack--gutter-m\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-e-text nova-legacy-e-text--size-l nova-legacy-e-text--family-sans-serif nova-legacy-e-text--spacing-none nova-legacy-e-text--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-text--clamp-2 nova-legacy-v-publication-item__title\"><a class=\"nova-legacy-e-link nova-legacy-e-link--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-link--theme-bare\" href=\"publication/252559134_Decision_Improvement_through_Multi-Criteria_Strategies_in_Mobile_Location-Based_Services\">Decision Improvement through Multi-Criteria Strategies in Mobile Location-Based Services</a></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta-left\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-e-badge nova-legacy-e-badge--color-green nova-legacy-e-badge--display-block nova-legacy-e-badge--luminosity-high nova-legacy-e-badge--size-l nova-legacy-e-badge--theme-solid nova-legacy-e-badge--radius-m nova-legacy-v-publication-item__type\">Article</span></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta-left\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-e-badge nova-legacy-e-badge--color-green nova-legacy-e-badge--display-block nova-legacy-e-badge--luminosity-medium nova-legacy-e-badge--size-l nova-legacy-e-badge--theme-ghost no