A new computer system changes how its customers work. In developing such system, it also means designing not only the system itself but also the new work practice it will support. In this discussion, the relationship created through Contextual Inquiry is described. The process of making a relationship fit the needs of design is demonstrated and the interaction between a designer and a customer is shown. The ways by which a closer relationship between designer and customer support a larger collaborative relationship between the design team and the community it supports are suggested.</span></div></div></div></div><footer class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__footer\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__footer-actions\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-pack nova-legacy-o-pack--gutter-m nova-legacy-o-pack--width-auto nova-legacy-o-pack--vertical-align-middle\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-pack__item nova-legacy-v-publication-item__footer-button-group\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-button-group nova-legacy-c-button-group--gutter-m nova-legacy-c-button-group--orientation-horizontal nova-legacy-c-button-group--width-auto nova-legacy-v-publication-item__actions\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-button-group__item\"><a class=\"nova-legacy-c-button nova-legacy-c-button--align-center nova-legacy-c-button--radius-m nova-legacy-c-button--size-s nova-legacy-c-button--color-blue nova-legacy-c-button--theme-bare nova-legacy-c-button--width-auto nova-legacy-v-publication-item__action\" href=\"publication/220422435_Apprenticing_with_the_Customer\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-c-button__label\">View</span></a></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-c-button-group__item\"><button class=\"nova-legacy-c-button nova-legacy-c-button--align-center nova-legacy-c-button--radius-m nova-legacy-c-button--size-s nova-legacy-c-button--color-blue nova-legacy-c-button--theme-bare nova-legacy-c-button--width-auto nova-legacy-v-publication-item__action\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-c-button__label\"><span class=\" js-lite-click\" data-lite=\"{&quot;click&quot;:[{&quot;t&quot;:&quot;.js-target-abstract-61a68d3838eca&quot;,&quot;a&quot;:&quot;tc(lite-page-hidden)&quot;},{&quot;t&quot;:&quot;self&quot;,&quot;a&quot;:&quot;tc(lite-page-hidden)&quot;}]}\">Show abstract</span></span></button></div></div></div></div></div></footer></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item publication-citations__item publication-citations__item--redesign\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-citation-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack nova-legacy-o-stack--gutter-m nova-legacy-o-stack--spacing-none nova-legacy-o-stack--no-gutter-outside\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-o-stack__item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-citation-item__context-source\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item nova-legacy-v-publication-item--size-m gtm-reference-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__body\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack--gutter-m\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-e-text nova-legacy-e-text--size-l nova-legacy-e-text--family-sans-serif nova-legacy-e-text--spacing-none nova-legacy-e-text--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-text--clamp-2 nova-legacy-v-publication-item__title\"><a class=\"nova-legacy-e-link nova-legacy-e-link--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-link--theme-bare\" href=\"publication/220382600_Usability_engineering_turns_10\">Usability engineering turns 10</a></div></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack-item\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta\"><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta-left\"><span class=\"nova-legacy-e-badge nova-legacy-e-badge--color-green nova-legacy-e-badge--display-block nova-legacy-e-badge--luminosity-high nova-legacy-e-badge--size-l nova-legacy-e-badge--theme-solid nova-legacy-e-badge--radius-m nova-legacy-v-publication-item__type\">Article</span></div><div class=\"nova-legacy-v-publication-